&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The use of ligature rests wholly on the scribe’s preference at the time of writing. For example, we can see him write the letters E+T either as ligature or separately at different locations on the folio:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table&gt;
&lt;thead&gt;
